high_descs: turn around, walk to the vanity on the right
open the second from the right cabinet door, take the green cloth out
turn right, turn left to the counter
put the cloth in the sink, wash the cloth, take the cloth out
open the second from the right cabinet door, put the cloth in, close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: wash the cloth from the cabinet, put it back

high_descs: Turn left and face the sink.
Take the green cloth from the cabinet below the sink.
Place the green cloth in the sink.
Rinse the green cloth in the sink.
Place the cloth back in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the clean cloth back in the original cabinet.

high_descs: Walk to the sink on the right.
Open the lower left drawer, and take the green towel out.
Position yourself in front of the sink.
Place the towel under the faucet to soak it.
Go back to the drawer that you got the towel out of.
Place the wet towel back in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Get a towel out of the drawer to soak it, then put it back in the drawer.
